    "In addition, a decision must be taken on whether to use an application or 360º video, and, in either case, whether to develop it, to outsource the process, or to use an existing source.",
    "If the application is to be developed, some steps will be required: to select the engine, the type and the form of interaction, the device in which the application will be run, and the physiological data that are extracted.",
    "The Execution stage was divided into two phases: design of the experience and its performance.",
    "The first points to be decided for the design of the experience is sample size and its organization into groups, as well as whether a control group will be included in the experience for a comparison of the results.",
    "Then, the experience is performed under the supervision of researchers."
